# Learner state is PERSONAL, MUTABLE runtime data — never committed (PR-9).
# The engine (cc_spine/learner_state.py) and schemas are committed; the state is not.
# Synthetic fixtures under spine/tests/fixtures/ are the ONLY learner-state-shaped data
# allowed in the repo (they carry no real study history and no PII).
